    <div class="content"><p>I'm not assuming that the Centurion is actually standing guard as Ellen resurrects in the tub. It could be an editing fakeout using a shot from another part of the episode, perhaps a scene with a Centurion on the rebel baseship. That would be par for the course for SciFi's previews. I could see an intriguing storyline either way: she resurrects on a modern Cylon ship with one or more of the Seven around (Cavil?), or she resurrects in a secret Final Five facility and makes her way back to the Cylon or Colonial fleet.</p>
<p>But I do think Ellen will be back for real and will probably play a major part in the rest of the story.</p>
